Speed, claro.


33
00:02:13.536 --> 00:02:14.219
Tab Hunter!

34
00:02:15.471 --> 00:02:17.292
Me diga onde eu posso
encontrar Tab Hunter.


35
00:02:17.407 --> 00:02:18.204
Sem problemas.

36
00:02:18.274 --> 00:02:19.037
Nossa, obrigado!

37
00:02:19.108 --> 00:02:20.292
